{"word":"H1548 - גָּלַח - gâlach - gaw-lakh' - Poll - தலை","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>גָּלַח"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>gâlach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>gaw-lakh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Poll / தலை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சிரை, சவரம் பண்ணு, மொட்பைபடி, கத்தரி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to poll, to shave, to shave off, to be bald"},{"paragraph":"a) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to shave"},{"paragraph":"2) to shave off"},{"paragraph":"3) (figurative of devastation)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Pual) to be shaven"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hithpael) to shave oneself"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>be bald</i>, that is, (causatively) to <i>shave</i>; figuratively to <i>lay waste: - </i>poll, shave (off)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}